SQL_STMT_U.val: select count (*) from Angebotkopf WITH(NOLOCK) where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4 and kundennr=:5 and datum>=':6' and datum<=':7'
select count (*) from KUNDEN_BESUCHSBERICHT WITH(NOLOCK) where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4 and kdnr=:5 and besuch_am>=':6' and besuch_am<=':7'
select count (*) from AUFTRAGKOPF WITH(NOLOCK) where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4 and kunden_nr=:5 and auftragsdatum>=':6' and auftragsdatum<=':7'
delete kunden_branchen where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4 and kdnr=:5
delete kunden_wettbewerber where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4 and kdnr=:5
select max (lfdnr) from kunden_besuchsbericht WITH(NOLOCK) where ebene1=:1 and ebene2=:2 and ebene3=:3 and ebene4=:4
